# Industrial Request Intelligence Platform Backend

Base backend scaffold with a modular architecture ready to grow into a SaaS industrial platform.

## Run locally

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -e .[dev]
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

## Run tests

```bash
pytest
```

